[Camera Charge Always Max]
author=bungholio
description=No ghost ever survives a 2nd shot. It causes 250 damage and gives you 9999 points for every shot that you take that damages a ghost.
Right next to that address is also the currently equipped film amount too. It was either 00252ACA or 00252ACB.
patch=1,EE,00252AC8,extended,000000FF

