patch=1,EE,1026C7F8,extended,00000000

[Minimum Light Source Radius]
author=bungholio
description=It doesn&#039;t really increase the brightness. It changes how far light extends from light sources. If you set it to minimum, it&#039;s definitely not pitch black but you will have trouble seeing some stuff unless you are walking around while looking through your camera.


There are quite a bit of different visual modifications from address 0026c7e0 to 0026c820. They aren&#039;t that special. One of them made a translucent stretched image of other camera viewpoints on the screen, another messed with how dim lights were, and another only worked with the black and white visual mode to increase that weird old static looking noise effect on the screen.
patch=1,EE,1026C7F8,extended,0000FFFF

